title: American Greetings 200 Sheet Bulk White Tissue Paper for Mother’s Day, Father’s Day, Graduation, Birthdays and All Occasions
description: Stock up on gift tissue paper for all your celebration needs! This convenient bulk tissue paper package includes 200 sheets of white tissue you can keep on hand for fluffing up gift presentations, crafting, decorating, place settings, gift baskets and more. For a quick decorating idea, shape the gift-wrap tissue paper into tissue paper balls and tissue paper garland! Save leftover tissue for future holidays, birthdays and any special occasion. It’s a must-have item for any gift packaging supply!
